# Example 1 — Hello DevKit
# This creates a demo file, modifies it, and cleans up.

:CREATE demo/hello.txt
Hello from DevKit!
This is line 2.
Line 3 has TODO: replace me.
:END

:REPLACE demo/hello.txt
FIND:
TODO: replace me.
WITH:
✓ Replaced by DevKit.
:END

:APPEND demo/hello.txt
Line 4 appended.
:END

:INFO demo/hello.txt
:READ demo/hello.txt
